# OPS/app/100 — a minimal landing page for the bound hostname.
#
# The AI gateway hangs off the SAME hostname as ordinary web traffic:
# POST /v1/messages is intercepted by the inlet, everything else routes
# here like any web request. This one-op stack proves the two coexist.
WHEN @src == "http"
  EMIT @web.res.status = 200,
       @web.res.headers.content-type.0 = "text/plain; charset=utf-8",
       @web.res.body = b64"llm gateway demo — POST /v1/messages speaks Anthropic Messages\n",
       @halt = true
